SVMTool++ uses the cmake (1) build system.

To build, just do the following steps:
- create a folder where to build:
% mkdir /path/to/build/folder
- move to this folder:
% cd /path/to/build/folder
- run cmake, optionaly specifying a build type (Release, RelWithDebInfo or
Debug) and an installation directory (default is specific to you system,
usualy /usr/local):
% cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/path/to/install/dir /path/to/svmtool
- run make:
% make
- install:
% make install


(1) http://www.cmake.org/